    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Honest fair-condition example that looks usable as-is but shows its age throughout. The body, paint, and trim are presentable from a distance, though there are noticeable cosmetic flaws, imperfections, and general wear consistent with an older driver. The interior is complete and functional, but expect visible wear and a used, lived-in appearance rather than a fresh or highly detailed presentation. Overall, this is the kind of car for someone who wants an affordable entry point and a straightforward driver they can enjoy while improving over time.",
      "price": 18900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Solid good-condition example that presents well and appears to be a well-kept driver. The paint, trim, and interior should show nicely overall, with only the kind of minor age-related wear and small imperfections you\u2019d expect from a car that has been used and cared for rather than over-restored. It looks like the sort of car you can enjoy right away, with a cleaner, more sorted appearance than a fair-condition driver, but it should not be mistaken for a mint or concours-level example. A buyer can expect a respectable, attractive car that is suitable for regular enjoyment, with some normal cosmetic and mechanical aging still possible upon close inspection.",
      "price": 29900.0,
