      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this car is a great fit for someone looking for cheap wheels, a project, or dependable basic transport without spending a fortune. It\u2019s not perfect and shows its age, but it still has plenty to offer for the right buyer. If you want something budget-friendly with room to make it your own, this could be a solid pick.",
